ormal use within the home.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-75_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-77_">The damage existed prior to use by the customer and is the result of production or faulty workmanship/materials which are not attributable to transportation.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-78_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-80_">Cracks, dents, or damage to the foam have arisen despite proper use and handling. </span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-81_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-83_">The mattress was laid upon a flat, supportive surface during use. </span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-84_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-86_">There is pre-existing damage to the zipper. </span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-87_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-89_">The indentations are greater than 1.5 inches (when compared with the surrounding mattress area) that permanently do not return to their normal height after the release of pressure.*</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-90_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-92_">Note: The removable cover of the Emma mattress is also warranted for 10 years, assuming normal use. If the application of warranty is approved, Emma will replace the cover, free of charge to the original purchaser.</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-93_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bSqaIl iXTDAP pf-94_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-96_">Not Covered</span></h6><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-gHjyzD dQAIat pf-97_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-98_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-100_">Product was sold by an unauthorized retailer or resold after being used by the original owner.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-101_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-103_">The use of the mattress was for a medical patient of any kind.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-104_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-106_">Damage is the result of abnormal treatment of the product, misuse, or neglect. (Emma shall have the authority to determine such causes of the damage). This includes, but is not limited to,</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-107_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-109_">Odors, burns, cuts, infestation, or bodily fluids which are present at the time of the application of warranty.&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-110_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-112_">The color change of the fabric after exposure to light or prolonged periods of usage.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-113_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-115_">Personal preference when it comes to comfort, height, or design. </span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-116_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-118_">Damage that has arisen due to transportation (not including initial delivery from Emma)</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-119_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-121_">Increase in softness due to long term use.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-122_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-124_">Wear-and-tear prompted by cleaning and laundering.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-125_"><span da